        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Safe Disposal of Opioids Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Justice to award grants to establish or maintain disposal sites for unwanted prescription medications.</p> <p>Additionally, the bill imposes a fee on the sale of an active opioid by the manufacturer, producer, or importer. The Department of Health and Human Services must establish a mechanism to provide discounts to patients to ensure that they do not pay the fee.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
